<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>시세 가져오기 - PRAVANG</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/nav') %>
<div class="container">
  <div class="page-title">외부 시세 가져오기 <span class="vuln-tag">A10 - SSRF</span></div>

  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">URL에서 시세 데이터 가져오기</div>
      <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/admin/price-fetch">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>시세 API URL (검증 없음)</label>
          <input type="text" name="url" value="<% if (typeof fetchedUrl !== 'undefined') { %><%= fetchedUrl %><% } %>" placeholder="http://api.example.com/prices">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">가져오기</button>
      </form>

      <% if (result) { %>
      <div style="margin-top:16px">
        <div class="card-title">응답 결과</div>
        <pre class="code-block"><%= result %></pre>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">SSRF 테스트 페이로드</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:2">
        내부 서버 접근:<br>
        <code>http://localhost:3000</code><br>
        <code>http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/users</code><br>
        <code>http://127.0.0.1:3000/admin</code><br><br>
        클라우드 메타데이터:<br>
        <code>http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/</code><br>
        <code>http://metadata.google.internal/</code><br><br>
        파일 프로토콜:<br>
        <code>file:///etc/passwd</code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
